1. Kada *se uklopim* u novi posao, biće mi lakše. (When I *fit in* to the new job, it will be easier for me.)
2. On *se uklapa* u društvo lako. (He *blends in* with society easily.)
3. Njihov stil života *se ne uklapa* u moje ideale. (Their lifestyle *doesn't match* my ideals.)
4. Kako *se uklopiš* u ovu haljinu? (How does it *fit* you in this dress?)
5. Molim vas da *uklopite* svoje termine sa terminom sastanka. (Please *coordinate* your schedule with the meeting time.)
6. Njihove riječi *se ne uklapaju* sa njihovim postupcima. (Their words *don't correspond* with their actions.)
7. Kao novi zaposleni, pokušaću da *se uklopim* u tim i postanem produktivan. (As a new employee, I will try to *adapt* to the team and become productive.)